{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"我们欢呼　我们歌唱","authors":["武义德　连高　赵芳才"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":4,"day":22}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们欢呼　我们歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔朗诵诗〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部战士　武义德　连高　赵芳才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旭日东升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒万丈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人如潮涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声嘹亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京市革命委员会成立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一声春雷响彻四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万面红旗迎风飞舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万颗红心激动跳荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛主席万岁！万万岁！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲四海翻腾着巨浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界革命的中心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界革命人民的希望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命的发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"源地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大领袖毛主席居住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党内一小撮走资本主义道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路的当权派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄图把北京变成资本主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复辟的温床。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们颠倒黑白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"混淆是非，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结党营私，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负隅顽抗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们煽阴风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放暗箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶毒攻击毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶毒攻击党中央。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席点燃了革命烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把无产阶级文化大革命道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路照亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风劲吹天地动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民斗志昂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席天安门上挥巨手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农兵奋起千钧棒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过了艰苦的阶级大搏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把旧市委反革命修正主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集团彻底埋葬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破了重重困难险阻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把污泥浊水一扫而光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们取得了一个又一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我们无穷的力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最最敬爱的伟大领袖毛主"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"席啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心中最红最红的红太"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们深知胜利来之不易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里征途还充满了惊涛骇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚决响应您的伟大号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把您的教导牢记心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念念不忘阶级斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"念念不忘无产阶级专政，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捍卫革命的“三结合”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的大权我们牢牢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狠抓革命，猛促生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把伟大祖国建设得更加繁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荣富强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大破“私”字，大立“公”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让毛泽东思想深深地扎根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提高警惕，握紧枪杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一切害人虫统统扫光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死保卫毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓死捍卫党中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀祖国，放眼世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让光焰无际的毛泽东思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把世界照得通红、通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"name":"革命三结合","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}